OL,3,CChannel Islanders see stunning show of
OL,4,Ccolour in rare weather event
OL,6,FChannel Islanders have been treated to
OL,7,Fa rare and spectacular show as the
OL,8,Fdark skies turned technicolour across
OL,9,Fboth Bailiwicks on Monday night.
OL,11,FThe Aurora Borealis or Northern Lights
OL,12,Fare more commonly seen in Scotland but
OL,13,Fcombined with the Perseid meteor
OL,14,Fshower for a dramatic natural display
OL,15,Facross the British Isles.
OL,17,FThe dazzling demonstration was
OL,18,Fcaptured on camera by a number of
OL,19,Fpeople who stayed up to see it into
OL,20,Fthe early hours of Tuesday morning (13
OL,21,FAugust).
